jp.co.tanita.comm.ble

Class TNTDeviceInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.co.tanita.comm.ble.TNTDeviceInformation

  • public class TNTDeviceInformation
extends java.lang.Object
    The property class that retains device information.

    This class retains common device information and individual device information. You can access individual device information,to invoke the method which is #getExtInfo(String).
